Text: RE Electric Power Conf Cc Thank you Kevin Attached please find further information on the Starline Technology I have seen this process in action and believe it to be a great tool for rehabilitating gas mains and services As discussed I have included contact information for our Director of this technology Ted Fiala You will find it in the PowerPoint presentation If chosen to speak we would be more than happy to work on developing a presentation based on our experiences with major utility players and perhaps be able to bring them along to discuss the technology as well Thank you very much for reviewing the information and I look forward to hearing from you Catherine Spurway Marketing Services Coordinator Exelon Infrastructure Services Yale Avenue Morton PA Ph Fax starine write updoc Starline Presentation ppt Original Message From Hyatt Kevin mailtoKevin NRONcom Sent Tuesday October PM To Subject Electric Power Conf Message Untitled Attachment File NGI Singlespdf File EPSinglespdf
